Definition: marked by rude or peremptory shortness
Example: try to cultivate a less brusque manner; a curt reply; the salesgirl was very short with him
Synonyms: noun, attribute, brusqueness, brusk, curt, curtness, short, p, shortness, marked, by, rude, or, peremptory, try, to, cultivate, a, less, manner, reply, the, salesgirl, was, very, with, him
Category: adj.all
